title: CFB SATURDAY WEEK 3 ONE DAY AWAY
description:
Jason Fitz, Joey Galloway, and David Pollack breakdown their expectations for marquee Week 3 matchups in Florida vs Alabama and Auburn vs Penn State. The crew also talks about what the results of Week 3 could mean for ranked teams.
